title: Eastern European Train Pass By Sound Effect Pack
description: The lords of rails are rolling loudly day and night fully loaded with passengers, containers or machines. This collection contains of 100 sounds of Eastern European trains passing by. Warning: horns can be pretty loud sometimes !
longDescription:
The lords of rails are rolling loudly day and night fully loaded with passengers, containers or machines. This collection contains of 100 sounds of Eastern European trains passing by. Warning: horns can be pretty loud sometimes !


I have always loved the different sounds of trains as they pass by or the sound of their loud horns. I recorded these sounds for many days to create this sound effect pack, which is perfect for train scenes.


This sound effect collection is ideal for use in game software, applications, commercials, movies, TV shows,

videos, animation, and any other entertainment industry where a high-quality audio effect is essential.
technicalDetails:
Features:

  •  100 Train Pass By sound effect.
  • For productions where trains appear. 

Number of Audio Waves: 100

Number of Audio Cues: 100

Sample rate / bit rate: 44,100 Hz

Do Sound FX loop: No

Minutes of audio provided: 01hr 11min 52sec

Supported Development Platforms:

Mac: Yes
